Game information:

Sins of a Solar Empire: Rebellion - the first independent addition to
the space strategy Sins of a Solar Empire, which was published in 2008.
Addition provides access to new factions, improves the graphics, adds
a new victory conditions, and a host of new vehicles. Among the new
ships should be singled out deadly swinger class Titan,
able to cope with an enemy fleet.
